title: Annie96 Is Typing
itunes:title: Annie96 Is Typing
itunes:subtitle: The Creepypasta Anthology
description:
We all do it. How many times a day do you text or instant message your friends and family? How often do you really think about what is happening on the other side? Friends McDavey and Annie96 fine out exactly how terrifying a chat can become...
